---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
---
<Site
  title="Case Studies"
  description="Real teams running leaner with Kanban Live — from a £5M+ aerospace win at Spectech to NHS ward stock and two-tier manufacturing replenishment."
>
  <!-- ============ HEADER ============ -->
  <header style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px 32px 8px;">
    <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent);">Case studies</div>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:clamp(32px,4.6vw,50px); line-height:1.06; letter-spacing:-.03em; margin:14px 0 0; color:var(--text); max-width:760px; text-wrap:balance;">Real teams, running leaner with Kanban Live</h1>
  </header>

  <!-- ============ FEATURED CASE STUDY ============ -->
  <section style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px 32px 8px;">
    <div class="kl-cs" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr; gap:0; border-radius:22px; overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--border); box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);">
      <div style="background:var(--surface); padding:clamp(32px,4vw,52px);">
        <span style="display:inline-block; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1F7D4D; background:rgba(53,164,107,.14); padding:5px 12px; border-radius:999px;">Aerospace &amp; defence</span>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:clamp(24px,2.8vw,32px); line-height:1.18; letter-spacing:-.02em; margin:18px 0 0; color:var(--text); text-wrap:balance;">Kanban Live helps Spectech secure over £5&nbsp;million in aerospace contracts</h2>
        <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; color:var(--text-2); margin:16px 0 0;">Spectech provide aviation spares to the aerospace and defence industries and have used Kanban Live for the past three years to gain tighter control and visibility of their inventory across sites in the UK, France and North America. Read the case study to find out how we helped them win over £5 million in new contracts.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="kl-lift" style="display:inline-block; text-decoration:none; margin-top:26px; background:var(--accent); color:var(--accent-ink); font-size:15px; font-weight:600; padding:13px 24px; border-radius:11px; box-shadow:0 10px 24px -8px var(--accent);">Read the case study</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#211C16; padding:clamp(32px,4vw,52px); display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; gap:28px;">
        <div>
          <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:44px; letter-spacing:-.02em; color:var(--accent-2);">£5M+</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px; color:#A89E90; margin-top:4px;">in new contracts secured</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:44px; letter-spacing:-.02em; color:#F6F2EC;">3 sites</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px; color:#A89E90; margin-top:4px;">UK · France · North America</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:44px; letter-spacing:-.02em; color:#F6F2EC;">3 years</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px; color:#A89E90; margin-top:4px;">of tighter inventory control</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ QUOTE ============ -->
  <section style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:44px 32px;">
    <div style="background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:22px; padding:clamp(32px,5vw,56px); box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
      <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:52px; line-height:1; color:var(--accent-2); font-weight:700;">"</div>
      <blockquote style="margin:6px 0 0; font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:500; font-size:clamp(20px,2.6vw,30px); line-height:1.34; letter-spacing:-.01em; color:var(--text); max-width:900px; text-wrap:balance;">Kanban Live helped us secure major contracts with a number of high-profile aerospace clients. It's a foolproof system and, quite simply, the best use of technology in our business today.</blockquote>
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-top:26px;">
        <span style="width:44px; height:44px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--accent-2); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:700; color:#4A2E00;">CO</span>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:700; color:var(--text); font-size:15px;">Chris Osborne</div>
          <div style="color:var(--text-3); font-size:14px;">Operations Director, Spectech</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ MORE STORIES ============ -->
  <section style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:8px 32px 0;">
    <div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:20px;">More stories</div>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr)); gap:16px;">

      <div style="background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:18px; padding:28px; box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
        <span style="display:inline-block; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#B47100; background:rgba(245,166,35,.16); padding:5px 12px; border-radius:999px;">Healthcare</span>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:21px; line-height:1.2; letter-spacing:-.01em; margin:16px 0 0; color:var(--text);">Ward stock that never runs dry — or expires unseen</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px; line-height:1.55; color:var(--text-2); margin:12px 0 0;">An NHS trust moved supply-room shelves onto min–max levels with GS1 lot and expiry capture. Nurses take stock; Kanban Live picks earliest-expiry first, flags use-by dates ahead of time, and drafts the week's purchase orders automatically.</p>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:24px; margin-top:20px;">
          <div><div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; color:var(--accent);">FEFO</div><div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-3);">earliest expiry, picked first</div></div>
          <div><div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; color:var(--text);">1 scan</div><div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-3);">product + lot + expiry</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:18px; padding:28px; box-shadow:var(--shadow);">
        <span style="display:inline-block; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#1F7D4D; background:rgba(53,164,107,.14); padding:5px 12px; border-radius:999px;">Manufacturing &amp; MRO</span>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:21px; line-height:1.2; letter-spacing:-.01em; margin:16px 0 0; color:var(--text);">Direct line feed, refilled from one warehouse</h3>
        <p style="font-size:15px; line-height:1.55; color:var(--text-2); margin:12px 0 0;">An automotive supplier runs kanban bins at customer sites on transfer orders from a central warehouse — while the warehouse itself replenishes by purchase order. One engine, two tiers: bins refill by transfer, the warehouse refills by purchase, no one over-orders.</p>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:24px; margin-top:20px;">
          <div><div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; color:var(--accent);">2 tiers</div><div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-3);">transfer + purchase</div></div>
          <div><div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:26px; color:var(--text);">1 order</div><div style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-3);">per supplier, per run</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ CTA ============ -->
  <section style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:44px 32px 64px;">
    <div style="background:var(--surface-2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:20px; padding:40px; text-align:center;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-weight:600; font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,34px); letter-spacing:-.02em; margin:0; color:var(--text);">Could your team be next?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px; color:var(--text-2); margin:14px auto 0; max-width:480px;">Start a free trial or request a demo and we'll show you how Kanban Live fits your shop floor.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:14px; justify-content:center; margin-top:24px;">
        <a href="/pricing/" class="kl-lift-2" style="text-decoration:none; background:var(--accent); color:var(--accent-ink); font-size:16px; font-weight:600; padding:14px 26px; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 10px 24px -8px var(--accent);">See plans &amp; pricing</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="kl-lift-2" style="text-decoration:none; background:var(--surface); color:var(--text); font-size:16px; font-weight:600; padding:14px 26px; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--border-strong);">Request a free demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
